title: Heindrich Swanepol
text:
Heindrich Swanepol is a <a href="Paralympic">Paralympic</a> <a href="track%20and%20field">athlete</a> from <a href="Great%20Britain">Great Britain</a> competing mainly in category F12 javelin events.
Heindrich won a bronze medal in the F12 javelin at the <a href="2000%20Summer%20Paralympics">2000 Summer Paralympics</a> in <a href="Sydney">Sydney</a>.
